headline: Walbridge Recognized as 2024 Supplier of the Year and Overdrive Award Winner by General Motors
summary: General Motors presented Walbridge with a 2024 Supplier of the Year and Overdrive Award at GM's 33rd annual Supplier of the Year event in Phoenix, Arizona on April 8, 2025. Walbridge is one of only four suppliers to receive both awards this year.
